Package: hart-os
Version: 1.0.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: python3.10, python3.10-venv, python3-pip, ufw, curl
Maintainer: Hevolve AI <team@hevolve.ai>
Homepage: https://hevolve.ai
Description: HART OS - Crowdsourced Agentic Intelligence Platform
 HART OS is a custom Linux distribution layer for running autonomous
 AI agents with crowdsourced compute, peer-to-peer federation,
 constitutional guardrails, and 90% revenue back to contributors.
 .
 Features:
  - 96 specialized AI agents across 10 categories
  - Recipe pattern: learn once, replay efficiently
  - Ed25519 signed peer-to-peer federation
  - Constitutional AI guardrails (33 immutable rules)
  - Local LLM inference (llama.cpp) + cloud fallback
  - Vision AI sidecar (MiniCPM)
  - Kids learning platform (105 built-in games)
  - WearOS companion support
